Model and TV personality Blue Mbombo served all sorts of fire during a recent trip to the Mother City. Of course it's impossible to go to Cape Town and not visit the ocean, and that meant Blue got to show off her smoking-hot figure. She also got some time to introspect and shared some of her thoughts with fans. "Every time I stand before a beautiful beach, its waves seem to whisper to me: If you choose the simple things and find joy in nature's simple treasures, life and living need not be so hard." Blue also served major booty envy!